{
  "texts": [
    "By fine-tuning the GPT model on materials-science-specific QA data, we enhance its ability to comprehend and extract relevant information from the scientific literature.",
    "Through our experiments and evaluations, we validate the effectiveness of GPT-enabled MLP models, analysing their cost, reliability, and accuracy to advance materials science research.",
    "Furthermore, we discuss the implications of GPT-enabled models for practical tasks, such as entity tagging and annotation evaluation, shedding light on the efficacy and practicality of this approach.",
    "In summary, our research presents a significant advancement in MLP through the integration of GPT models.",
    "By leveraging the capabilities of GPT, we aim to overcome limitations in its practical applicability and performance, opening new avenues for extracting knowledge from materials science literature."
  ]
}